{"tid":1957439,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"肺疫危機下 美國首間小型銀行倒閉","createTime":"2020-04-04T02:41:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T02:41:38.000Z","uid":82340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7a7d5b2f0c1968002265106e1786313e789b8574","tid":1957439,"uid":82340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T02:41:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2428051\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F2428051&d=dfx5yx0%2Fy135WOof7TdQyhOHaT3cO7pga%2FagQaCgUd0%3D&h=bd8f8f2f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2428051</a><br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情爆發以來，美國出現首宗銀行倒閉個案。<br />\n<br />\n聯邦存款保障機構(FDIC)宣布，已經接管位於西弗吉尼亞州的小型銀行The First State Bank of Barboursville。西弗吉尼亞州的金融機構監管部門較早時關閉該銀行。<br />\n<br />\nFirst State Bank旗下有4間分行，集團資產總值為1.52億美元。根據公告，MVB Bank將接管First State Bank的1.395億美元存款，4間分行周一起將易名MVB Bank，冀繼續經營。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n升! <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}